<plot>Broken Fidelity is a surreal drama about a wife, Diane who receives a mysterious videotape that contains footage of her affair. Meanwhile a photographer is watching her every move inside a movie theater. Broken Fidelity is in abstract film about mistaken identity, the creative process, the manipulation of art, guilt, and blackmail.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?083876</url></doc>
